data.description: Looking for a log home?  Take a look at this one located on 1.44 acres at 454 Stingray Lane, Hartsville SC on a cove of Lake Robinson in Chesterfield County. Approximately 1500 square feet on main level with open floor plan.  Living area with fireplace, dining area, kitchen with pantry and island, utility room.  Split bedroom floorplan with hall bath.   Master suite with jet tub, double vanities, and walk-in closet.  Mexican tile floors and carpet.  Heat pump seven years old.  Large front porch for swinging, rocking, relaxing!  Back deck with beautiful view of the lake.  Partially fenced area/garden area.  Blueberry bushes.  Approximately 750 square feet downstairs with open rec room/greatroom, fourth bedroom, bathroom.  Wall unit for heating and cooling.  Attached double garage with storage/work area.  Call today to view this unique property.
